data.description: 2 separately taxed lots, to equal 1.25+ acres. Must sell together. On city utilities.  Conveniently located. Walking distance to shopping and services. The back yard is partially fenced. Lots of trees in the back.  Partially covered back deck. Three sheds, two greenhouses, large garden area. investors and private party offers considered.
data.whatILove: A seasonal creek runs under the deck.  The wet bar and refrigerator in the bonus room currently being used as a shop, includes a power work table and door to outside.  A yard big enough for chickens, with an 8x8 chicken coop.  Enjoy the back deck with Humming birds, Blue Cardinals, Owls, Chickadees, Robins, Squirrels, Opossum, Rabbit, Raccoon.
